01:01:16.200 --> 01:01:21.130
Ada seorang pria aneh di sana. Dia mengintai, topinya diturunkan.

01:01:21.430 --> 01:01:22.540
Di depan gedung?

01:01:29.040 --> 01:01:30.040
Hai!

01:01:33.250 --> 01:01:34.410
Hei, berhenti di situ!

01:01:35.580 --> 01:01:37.480
